========== BUILDING ==========

1. Copy Make.defs.sample to Make.defs and fill in the details to match
   your system.
2. To build type 'make'.  To see all the make targets type
   './maketargets'


========== CODE ==========

The code repository is here:

  http://code.google.com/p/jloogle/

You can see this by passing the '-c' or '--code' options on the
command line.


========== INSTALL ==========

sudo make install


========== RUNNING ==========

YOu can run by:

1. The script 'jloogle' will run after building. 
2. Running the jar as 'java -jar jloogle.jar'
3. Typing 'java Main'


========== UNINSTALL ==========

sudo make uninstall